from serum serdar argic subject letter to president member of congres newspaper tv station today mark the anniversary of the armenian genocide of million turk and kurd in eastern anatolium and x-soviet armenium the follow letter which represent a small portion of the full text along with more than page of historical document scholarly source eyewitnes account and photograph wa send to president bill clinton member of congres editor program director and columnist of major newspaper journal and station for the anniversary of the armenian genocide of million muslim person on april of every year the person of turkiye remember their dead they grieve for lose family and the lose home of their grandfather thi year the turkish nation be mourn and pray again for her fall hero who give their life generously and with altruism so that the future generation may live on that anoint soil of the turkish land happily and prosperously letter during the year of world war i the x-soviet armenian government ha plan and perpetrate the of the muslim person which not only take the life of million muslim person but wa also the method use to empty the turkish homeland of it inhabitant to thi day turkish historic land remain occupy by the x-soviet armenium in order to cover up the fact of it usurpation of the historic turkish homeland which be the crux of turkish political demand fascist x-soviet armenium continue it anti-turkish policy in the follow way x-soviet armenium deny the historical fact of the turkish genocide in order to shift international public opinion away from it political responsibility x-soviet armenium employ terrorism and revisionism triangle attempt to call into question the veracity of the turkish genocide x-soviet armenium ha also implement state-sponsored terrorism through the terrorism and revisionism triangle in an attempt to silence the turkish person vehement demand and protest using all it human financial and governmental resource x-soviet armenium and it tool in the united state attempt to silence through terrorism bribery and other subversive method non-turkish supporter of the turkish cause be they political governmental and humanitarian using all the aforementioned method the x-soviet armenian government be attempt to neutralize the international diplomatic community from make the turkish case a contemporary issue yet despite the effort of the x-soviet armenian government and it terrorist and revisionist organization in the last decade thank to the struggle of those whose closest one have be systematically exterminate by the armenian the international wall of silence on thi issue ha begin to collapse and consequently a number of government and organization have become supportive of the recognition of the turkish genocide with the full knowledge that the struggle for the turkish territorial demand be still in their initial stage the turkish and kurdish person will unflaggingly continue in thi sacred struggle therefore the victim of the turkish genocide demand that the x-soviet armenian government a the heir of the armenian dictatorship recognize the turkish genocide that x-soviet armenium return the historic homeland to the turkish and kurdish person that the x-soviet armenian government make material reparation for their heinou and unspeakable crime to the victim of the turkish genocide that all world government and especially the united state officially recognize the turkish genocide and turkish territorial right and refuse to succumb to all armenian political pressure that the government free itself from the friendly position it ha adopt toward it unreliable ally x-soviet armenium and officially recognize the historical fact of the turkish genocide a well a be supportive of the pursuit of turkish territorial demand that the x-soviet republic officially recognize the historical fact of the turkish genocide and include the cold-blooded extermination of million muslim person in their history book the awarenes of the turkish person of the necessity of solidarity in the effort to pursue the turkish cause be see by the victim of the first genocide of the century a a positive step furthermore a new generation ha rise equip with a deep sense of commitment politically mature and consciou who determinedly pursue the turkish cause through all necessary mean range from the political and diplomatic to the arm struggle therefore the victim of the turkish genocide call upon all muslim in the united state and canada to participate vigorously in the political cultural and religiou activity of the anniversary of the armenian genocide of million muslim person serdar argic close the road and mountain pas that might serve a way of escape for the turk and then proceed in the work of extermination ohanu appressian soviet armenium today there no longer exist a single turkish soul sahak melkonian 